metadata.name: 0Stillbirth
metadata.description:
The Bindind of Isaac : Stillbirth will be a mod/expansion containing new items, trinkets, pickups, floors, enemies, bosses, characters, challenges, original soundtrack.
Stillbirth is a Community mod developed by Shisheyu's Twitch community.
Current Version : 0.01 (testing Mod Uploader with little content)
4 Passive Items :
* Money = Luck * Brave Shoe * Technology 0 * Hot Pizza Slice
3 Active Items :
* Dad's Beer * Golden Idol * Medusa's Head
